---
title: Easy As Smokey Fried Chicken & Bacon Cos Salad with Avocado & Roast Tomato Salsa
description: A crunchy cos salad is just what we need in the warmer weather. There’s only one way to improve on something so
fresh and delicious – add fried chicken! Throw it all together with some creamy avo and a few dollops of roast tomato salsa and you’re on to a winner!
